      "content": "I have completed the initial home loan assessment using affordability, credit, KYC and document checks.\n\nResult: Pre Approved\nRisk level: Low\nEstimated EMI: ₹48,598.10\nDTI ratio: 15.15%\nFOIR ratio: 15.15%\nLTV ratio: 24.35%\nKYC status: verified\nCIBIL status: acceptable\nDocument status: Complete\nMissing documents: None\n\nThis is an initial eligibility assessment only, not a final loan sanction.\n\nYou can ask me anything about this result, or type 'finish' to close the conversation."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "can u let me know what's the issue with my homeloan "
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Based on the assessment result, it seems that your home loan application is pre-approved, indicating that you meet the initial eligibility criteria. However, I would like to clarify that this is an initial eligibility assessment only, not a final loan sanction.\n\nTo confirm the loan sanction, the lender will need to conduct a detailed verification and final review of your application. The recommended actions are to proceed with the detailed verification and final lender review.\n\nIf you have any questions or concerns about the assessment result, feel free to ask."
    },
    {
